Cod are a type of fish that can be obtained by cooking raw cod on a fire or cooking range, requiring level 18 Cooking and granting 75 experience when successful. Players may burn a cod while cooking one, resulting in a burnt fish; the burn rate while cooking these will decrease as players reach higher Cooking levels. It will stop burning at Cooking level 49 on a range or level 51 on a fire.

Cod heals 7 Hitpoints when eaten. Cod is an ingredient in fish pies.

'''Cod''' are a type of [[fish]] that can be obtained by cooking [[raw cod]] on a [[fire]] or [[cooking range]], requiring level 18 [[Cooking]] and granting 75 experience when successful. Players may burn a cod while cooking one, resulting in a [[Burnt fish (trout)|burnt fish]]; the [[burn rate]] while cooking these will decrease as players reach higher Cooking levels. It will stop burning at [[Cooking]] level 49 on a range or level 51 on a fire.

Cod heals 7 [[Hitpoints]] when eaten. Cod is an ingredient in [[fish pie]]s.
